What are common COB errors and how do you resolve them?  --->
Typical errors: Account locked, missing OFS messages, product setup issues, suspense account mismatch.


Can you explain the phases of COB? --> 
A:
COB typically has 5 phases:
Start of Day (SOD) â€“ initialization, previous day closure, parameter setups.
Intraday Batch Jobs â€“ standing orders, payment runs, loan schedules.
End of Day (EOD) â€“ final postings, interest calculations, GL updates.
Start of Next Day â€“ move system date forward.
Reporting/Extracts â€“ regulatory, MIS, reconciliations.


